Modules needed
1) cuda/8.0.44   2) pgi/16.4   3) openmpi/1.10.2/pgi/16.4   4) cupti/8.0.44

module load cuda cupti pgi openmpi/1.10.2/pgi/16.4

To profile, either compile with -ta=nvidia,time or in the command line eneter 
export PGI_ACC_TIME=1
export ACC_NOTIFY=1
pgaccelinfo (to get details of the detected accelerator)




